1 Breaking Glass is a film that everyone aspiring to be in the music industry should see more than once . It is a very dark tale about the way a record company manipulates a singer to do things their way and to make as much money out of her as possible . Looking at some of today 's ' search for a star ' style TV shows on both in the UK and abroad I am always reminded of this film . Though not an expert on the subject , the winners of these shows tend to have one very big initial hit and then its downhill from there . This film predates these shows though the effect seems the same . After getting rid of her manager , played quite brilliantly by Phil Daniels , slowly but surely the record company changes her lyrics puts her on stimulants and she is eventually totally burnt out . You potential stars of tomorrow .... WATCH THIS AND BEWARE ! ! !
