s such . You should n't watch FSN thinking that it does n't present the viewer with the historic fact , just remember that this is adventure / fantasy series and not a documentary and enjoy this as long as you can . The ending is sudden and unexpected and if there were twice as many episodes I would have watched them in the same breath .
