t , the Sanctity of marriage and the family , as well a patriotic to our homeland and country . We are all different as well just like you can find different protestants , Presbyterians , methodist , baptist and Catholics . What 's important is our message and what we stand for . This movie trys to portray that but there is so much of Joseph 's life that ca n't be covered in a mere 2 hour movie . This was a really great show .
