hough they have dressed her so dowdy in most of the costumes she wears on the screen . Hugh Jackman is seen as Peter Lyman a sophisticated man about town with the right pedigree . He makes a good appearance in the movie as the man pursuing Ms. Johansson . Ian McShane plays the dead Fleet Street journalist on his way to eternity.<br /><br />"Scoop " is a light film for the hot and humid summer thanks to Woody Allen .
